data.description: Welcome to your dream home in beautiful Pueblo, Colorado! This charming 5-bedroom, 2-bath home with a detached garage is a rare find in this sought-after neighborhood. With its well-maintained exterior and a warm, inviting interior, this property is perfect for families and individuals alike. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the spacious and open floor plan that allows natural light to flood the living spaces. The living room is a cozy place to gather, for those chilly Colorado evenings. The adjacent dining area provides a perfect space for family meals and entertaining. Conveniently located in a friendly neighborhood, you'll have easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and all that Pueblo has to offer. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home sweet home. Schedule a showing today and make this property yours before it's gone!
